@base = http://localhost:3000

### Health check
GET {{base}}/healthz

### Readiness check
GET {{base}}/readyz

### Agent cards (A2A discovery)
GET {{base}}/.well-known/agent-cards

### Exploration status (sitemap + findings stats)
GET {{base}}/api/status

### Full sitemap
GET {{base}}/api/sitemap

### All findings
GET {{base}}/api/findings

### Findings filtered by URL
GET {{base}}/api/findings?url=http://forms:80

### All agent tasks
GET {{base}}/api/tasks
